      <title>马克龙签署 27 亿欧元战机协议，助力塞尔维亚巩固欧洲地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/macron-clinches-2-7-billion-warplane-deal-to-help-anchor-serbia-to-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着巴尔干国家加强与欧盟重要国家的关系并将其国防订单从传统合作伙伴俄罗斯转移，法国同意向塞尔维亚出售价值 27 亿欧元（30 亿美元）的战斗机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/macron-clinches-2-7-billion-warplane-deal-to-help-anchor-serbia-to-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 19:10:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国监管机构认为里夫斯有理由增加公共投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/uk-watchdog-sees-case-for-reeves-to-ramp-up-public-investment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政监管机构为新任财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 提供了大力进行公共投资的理由，因为人们担心她过于谨慎的预算可能会损害经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/uk-watchdog-sees-case-for-reeves-to-ramp-up-public-investment</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 18:15:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称其一架 F-16 战机在俄罗斯空袭中坠毁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ukraine-says-lost-f-16-jet-in-crash-during-russian-air-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰军方称，周一，其一架美国制造的 F-16 战斗机在试图击退俄罗斯空袭时坠毁，飞行员丧生。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/ukraine-says-lost-f-16-jet-in-crash-during-russian-air-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:59:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国称以色列允许暂停加沙地区脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/israel-to-allow-pauses-for-polio-vaccinations-in-gaza-un-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国一名高级官员表示，以色列将允许在加沙地带部分地区暂停人道主义战斗，以便联合国开展脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/israel-to-allow-pauses-for-polio-vaccinations-in-gaza-un-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:43:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>陆军为与特朗普团队对峙的阿灵顿公墓工作人员辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/army-defends-cemetery-staffer-who-confronted-trump-s-team</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国陆军为一名在参观阿灵顿国家公墓期间与唐纳德·特朗普竞选团队发生冲突的工作人员辩护，称她被“突然推到一边”，事件发生后又遭到“不公平的攻击”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/army-defends-cemetery-staffer-who-confronted-trump-s-team</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:17:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沃伦敦促华尔街监管机构解释执法行动减少的原因</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/warren-presses-wall-street-regulator-to-explain-decline-in-enforcement-actions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议员伊丽莎白·沃伦 (Elizabeth Warren) 正在向美国经纪交易商监管机构金融业监管局 (Finra) 施压，要求其说明为何近年来执法数量大幅下降，而金融业监管局声称，成功将不良行为者驱逐出行业是导致执法数量大幅下降的原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/warren-presses-wall-street-regulator-to-explain-decline-in-enforcement-actions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将宣布一项计划，让美国成为“加密之都”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-says-he-ll-announce-a-plan-to-make-us-the-crypto-capital-of-the-planet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普似乎正在更深入地涉足数字资产世界，他表示将公布计划，确保美国成为“全球加密之都”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-says-he-ll-announce-a-plan-to-make-us-the-crypto-capital-of-the-planet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>无论美国如何努力，欧盟都将推进俄罗斯资产计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/eu-to-move-forward-with-russian-asset-plan-regardless-of-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟最高外交官表示，无论美国提出什么问题，欧盟都将坚持承诺，从冻结的俄罗斯央行资产中向乌克兰提供援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/eu-to-move-forward-with-russian-asset-plan-regardless-of-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 09:55:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>胡塞武装称拖船可以拖走受损的红海油轮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/houthis-say-tugs-can-tow-away-stricken-red-sea-oil-tanker</link>
      <description><![CDATA[也门胡塞武装表示，他们将让拖船拖走他们上周在红海袭击的一艘油轮，此举可能有助于避免一场环境灾难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/houthis-say-tugs-can-tow-away-stricken-red-sea-oil-tanker</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 08:14:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
